Class EODatabaseInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • EODatabaseInterface

  • public class EODatabaseInterface
extends java.lang.Object
    The EODatabaseInterface handles all connections to the database. A connection to the database is only active, while the query to the dabase is executed. This means that each query call is realatively slow, but the upside is that multiple users can use the database at the same time.
